{"tid":2375624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎︱人大政協今往深圳接種疫苗 高永文：對疫苗有充分信心","createTime":"2021-01-22T07:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T07:35:14.000Z","uid":278449,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c06ad4c0466792ee965bd88b3d8fc029abea39aa","tid":2375624,"uid":278449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:23:05.000Z","msg":"為準備3月在北京舉行的人大政協兩會，多名港區人大代表及全國政協委員，今日啟程到深圳接種疫苗。有份接種的前食物及衞生局局長、全國政協委員高永文稱，不是自己決定接種哪一款疫苗，不過他對疫苗有充分信心。<br />\n<br />\n北京為3月初的兩會設下「雙重保險」，一方面日前多名人大政協先要接受病毒檢測，今日再到深圳接種疫苗，下月初會再接受檢測及打第二針。全國政協委員包括高永文、曾偉雄、林大輝等，今日到灣仔會展集合，乘旅遊巴前往深圳接種疫苗。<br />\n當中高永文被問到是否知道將會接種哪款疫苗，他指接種哪款疫苗不是他自己決定，但對疫苗有充分信心。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">有國家，無有怕！</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210122/BQ2BI4R65NH7JKIK7BHHAU6DS4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210122%2FBQ2BI4R65NH7JKIK7BHHAU6DS4%2F&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TfYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=6a96944e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210122%2FBQ2BI4R65NH7JKIK7BHHAU6DS4%2F&h=a60507e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210122/BQ2BI4R65NH7JKIK7BHHAU6DS4/</a>"},{"pid":"84076fa0e65889a94c1fed1821da9755433cdc5e","tid":2375624,"uid":266635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:25:14.000Z","msg":"好事,白老鼠越多越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d0de51272c27c98c336d69d176c9ca4b60b2d9","tid":2375624,"uid":184787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84076fa0e65889a94c1fed1821da9755433cdc5e","tid":2375624,"uid":266635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:25:14.000Z","msg":"好事,白老鼠越多越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"可能人地去打外國疫苗<img src=\"/assets